<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/cursor') %>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="cs-hero">
    <div class="cs-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="cs-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="cs-hero-content">
      <span class="cs-hero-eyebrow">Case Study</span>
      <h1 class="cs-hero-title">Building Brand<br>Advocacy</h1>
      <p class="cs-hero-sub">Podcast Production — Archive House Agency</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="cs-stats">
    <div class="cs-stats-inner">
      <div class="cs-stat reveal">
        <span class="cs-stat-num">500K+</span>
        <span class="cs-stat-label">Views</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-stat reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="cs-stat-num">24</span>
        <span class="cs-stat-label">Episodes Produced</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Media -->
  <section class="cs-media">
    <div class="cs-media-grid">
      <div class="cs-media-item reveal">
        <div class="cs-media-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-media-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="cs-media-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-media-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="cs-media-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About the Production -->
  <section class="cs-content">
    <div class="cs-content-inner reveal">
      <div class="cs-content-left">
        <span class="cs-content-eyebrow">The Production</span>
        <h2 class="cs-content-heading">How We<br>Built It</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-content-right">
        <p>Braxton Studios partnered with Archive House Agency to produce the Building Brand Advocacy podcast from the ground up. Our team handled the full end-to-end production pipeline — from pre-production planning and set design through to filming, editing, and final delivery.</p>
        <p>Every episode was crafted with a cinematic approach, bringing a premium visual standard to the podcast format. We managed multi-camera setups, lighting design, audio engineering, and post-production to ensure each episode felt polished and on-brand.</p>
        <p>The result was a series that not only resonated with the target audience but drove meaningful engagement, establishing Building Brand Advocacy as a standout voice in the brand marketing space.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <%- include('partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
